  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to develop a small, easily used device to detect a person's
      blood flow in their fingertips.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To develop a hand held touch-pad device for identification of individuals, to help with
      banking and, possibly for detection of anxiety. This is done by their fingerprint and, other
      digital anatomy and vascular biometrics.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
